        title Walletnotes
        link(href="http://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css", rel="stylesheet")
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="css/main.css")
        link(rel="icon" href="favicon.ico")
    body
        .wrapper
            .navbar.navbar-fixed-top(role="navigation")
                .container
                    .navbar-header
                        button.navbar-toggle(type="button", data-toggle="collapse", data-target=".navbar-collapse")
                            span.sr-only Toggle navigation
                            span.icon-bar
                            span.icon-bar
                            span.icon-bar
                        a#logo.navbar-brand(href="index.html")
                            img(src="img/logo.png", alt="Walletnotes logo", title="Walletnotes")
                    .navbar-collapse.collapse
                        ul.nav.navbar-nav
                            li.active
                                a(href="index.html") HOME
                            li
                                a(href="create.html") CREATE
                            li
                                a(href="redeem.html") REDEEM
            #message
                .container
                    h1
                        | BITCOINS WILL NEVER BE
                        br
                        | EASER FROM NOW!
                        br
                    p How easy to use can Bitcoin be for any person?
                    p From our point of view, it can be even easer, than cash.
                    button.btn(onclick="location.href='/create.html'") TRY NOW
            #just
                .container
                    h1 JUST CREATE IT, PRINT IT, SPEND IT
                    .row
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-1.col-md-6.col-md-offset-0
                            p
                                | No cash desk or ATM needed: just your Bitcoin wallet and printer. Merchant accepts bitcoins, but doesn&#8217;t accept Walletnotes? Hummm&#8230; He should think about this :) But never mind!
                            p
                                | You can redeem your walletnote to your Bitcoin wallet and spend bitcoins as usually you do &#8212; once again
                                | you don&#8217;t need cash desk or ATM.
                        .hand-wrapper.pull-right.right.col-xs-12.col-sm-5
                            img.pull-right(src="img/hand_up.png", alt="")
                            .hand-line
            #becomes
                .container
                    h1
                        | Bitcoins becomes the best gift
                        br
                        | with Walletnotes!
                    p
                        | Create the walletnote and gift it to your friend&#8217;s birthday or wedding. Even if he doesn&#8217;t have
                        br
                        | a Bitcoin wallet, he will receive those beautiful digital coins.
            #contribute
                .container
                    .mails-1.hidden-xs
                        img(src="img/m1_b.png", alt="", id="m1_b")
                        img(src="img/m1_m.png", alt="", id="m1_m")
                        img(src="img/m1_s.png", alt="", id="m1_s")

                    .content.col-xs-12.col-sm-12
                        h1
                            | Contribute in Bitcoin mass
                            br
                            | adoption with Walletnotes
                        p
                            | Make donations with Walletnotes to everybody, who doesn&#8217;t have bitcoin wallet
                            br
                            | or doesn&#8217;t even know about Bitcoin: by email, IM, or even direct SMS &#8212;
                            br
                            | no hard-to-type addresses or secret keys.
                    .mails-2.hidden-xs
                        img(src="img/m2_b.png", alt="", id="m2_b")
                        img(src="img/m2_m.png", alt="", id="m2_m")
                        img(src="img/m2_s.png", alt="", id="m2_s")
            #even
                .container
                    h1 EVEN SAFER THAN CASH
                    .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-sm-offset-2
                        p
                            | Each walletnote is protected with PIN-code. Just keep it safe: even if stolen, you can easily recover your Walletnotes and print them again.
                    .lock
                        img(src="img/lock.png", alt="")
            #simple
                .container
                    h1 SIMPLE TO VALIDATE
                    .col-xs-12.col-sm-12
                        p
                            | Agree to accept walletnote, but need to validate it? You can easily check it at redeem page, and transact bitcoins to your wallet at the same time. Don&#8217;t have or forgot your bitcoin address? Don&#8217;t worry! Just change PIN and proceed with the same walletnote &#8212; now it only belongs to you!
            #soulful
                .container
                    .row
                        h1 SOULFUL BITCOINS
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-7.col-md-8.pull-right
                            p
                                | Print the bundle of Walletnotes and feel yourself rich :)
                                | With Walletnotes, Bitcoin shifts from digital and cold to warm and tactile!
                        .hand-wrapper.pull-left.left.col-xs-12.col-sm-5.col-md-4
                            img(src="img/hand_down.png", alt="")
                            .hand-line.pull-left
            #footer
                .container
                    h1
                        | Walletnotes &#8212; YOUR CAP
                        br
                        | OF INVISIBILITY
                    p
                        | With Walletnotes you can turn your off all your devices and pay outside all networks.
                        br
                        | Feel the harmony of bitcoin&#8217;s privacy religion. No registration required for creating
                        br
                        | or redeeming Walletnotes!
                    button.btn(onclick="location.href='/create.html'") TRY NOW
            .push
        .bottomLine
            .bl-block
                .col-xs-12.col-sm-3.copyright Â© 2014 Walletnotes
